description: First Physicians Capital Group, Inc., through its subsidiaries, provides management, financial, ancillary healthcare, and IT services to the rural and community hospital market in the United States. The company offers management, staffing, lab, imaging, pharmacy, human resources, health information, cost reporting, financial planning, accounting, information technology, revenue cycle, supply chain, facility engineering, compliance, infection control, marketing, case management, quality, and continuing education services. The company was formerly known as Tri-Isthmus Group, Inc. and changed its name to First Physicians Capital Group, Inc. in September 2009. First Physicians Capital Group, Inc. was founded in 1980 and is based in Oklahoma City, California.
